    "desc": "Hindalco is one of India’s biggest aluminium manufacturing company and the world’s largest flat-rolled products player and recycler of aluminium. Hindalco’s state-of-art copper facility comprises a world-class copper smelter which is among Asia's largest custom smelters at a single location",
    "text": "CRM SRM Careers Follow us Contact us\nBUSINESSES\nINDUSTRIES\nSUSTAINABILITY\nINVESTORS\nOPERATIONS\nMEDIA\nABOUT US\nIndia’s first aluminium\nfreight rake developed by Hindalco\nRead more\n\n\nLATEST UPDATES View more updates...\n\"2021 stood out as the year when we delivered record shattering financial and operational performances\" – MD's letter to employees\nINVESTOR CENTRE\nQuotes by TradingView | As on last closing\nLATEST REPORTS\nHINDALCO AT A GLANCE\nOUR BRANDS\nOUR OPERATIONS\nResource Mining\nAlumina Refining\nAluminium smelters\nAluminium Downstream\nCopper Smelters\nLIFE AT HINDALCO\nAt Hindalco, we are always looking for talent, driven by commitment and passion to achieve and excel.\n\nCopyright @ 2022 Hindalco Industries Ltd. | Legal disclaimer | Beware of fraudulent job offers",
